{"tid":565794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【張浚生病逝】曾嘲港青於基本法起草時「細胞還未形成」","createTime":"2018-02-19T10:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T02:37:12.000Z","uid":20933,"like":277,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"ffaf6c7e4158783c7904e7ea9385d4852fbbb333","tid":565794,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180219/large/1519035911_4417.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180219%2Flarge%2F1519035911_4417.jpg&h=56861c5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報道指，新華社香港分社前副社長張浚生在內地病逝，終年82歲。2016年旺角騷亂後，張接受電視訪問時形容，該次騷亂是暴動，顯示港府教育青年人不足，加上港青受外部勢力策動，由前年開始的政改爭論，可看到港青不理解《基本法》，盲目行動，笑謂「《基本法》起草時，這些同學你那時候還不知道在哪裡，說難聽一點是細胞還未形成」。<br />\n<br />\n對於政改方案當年在立法會遭否決，他則指立會要配合政府施政，又批評有議員不論對錯「拉布」，令措施不能通過，要負很大責任，「你幾乎百分之百的反對，它（政府）怎麼辦」，但他不評論時任特首梁振英的施政表現，稱要留待市民評價。"},{"pid":"adc42bf9526c279d9de79c956704ce20bf5115e5","tid":565794,"uid":103156,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:35:53.000Z","msg":"又釘一隻。"},{"pid":"8a1b73318c245dabc5c62d4d24f3d45d16e83ae4","tid":565794,"uid":75745,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef5634b9f0e3752d8e7a635f96abba8bf7aea1c","tid":565794,"uid":162424,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:36:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26869aac7917237ca7f5a34adbeb2188de22059c","tid":565794,"uid":35706,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fbc9c3939028d6153cbd352d353c81db1a3427c","tid":565794,"uid":89037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl